    {
      "content": "Carefully review these requirements and best practices to ensure the high availability of hosts connected to your StorSimple device.",
      "pos": [
        11339,
        11471
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Configure StorSimple with [two-node file server cluster configurations][1].",
      "pos": [
        11475,
        11550
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "By removing single points of failure and building in redundancy on the host side, the entire solution becomes highly available.",
      "pos": [
        11551,
        11678
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Use Continuously available (CA) shares available with Windows Server 2012 (SMB 3.0) for high availability during failover of the storage controllers.",
      "pos": [
        11682,
        11831
      ]
    },
